text:
I had looked at all the jewelry stores in the area I just could not find that special one of a kind engagement ring. A sale womsn recomended Green Lake Jewelry may be able to make something.
I came in and meet with Ashley an told her what I was looking for. It was a wonderful experience watching the sketches being transformed into a beautiful engagement ring.
